) throws IOException {\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_PA5hsjSy5wFfyq1JvraEtAz7|fc_0ad15d2c73d32a450169f01b83ed80819384acfe3fd0846962", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/authenticator-test/reflect-config.json", "content": "[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"io_opentelemetry.opentelemetry_exporter_common.AuthenticatorTest$DelegateHolder\",\n    \"fields\": [\n      {\n        \"name\": \"delegate\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.4", "usage": {"input": 155, "output": 1789, "cacheRead": 34048, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35992, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777343344192, "responseId": "resp_0ad15d2c73d32a450169f01b70a5d08193ba63fee64b4326a5"}}
